To expedite communication and secure all functional sign off on the Argentine 
offshore power product I am circulating this overview of the product and its 
structure and remaining issues that still need to be addressed. Please submit 
comments as soon as possible so that we can secure the necessary approvals to 
load and launch this product.

Product Description
Product   Argentine Power Financial Swap
Obligation  Firm
Transaction Location Offshore Enron Offshore & Onshore Argentina Counterparty
Internal Counterparty  Enron North America
External Counterparties Generators, LDCs, Largest Industrials,  
Term   1 Year and less Intra month, Monthly, Seasonal
Volume   1MW and more
Index   Ezeiza
Currency  $US Dollars/MWh
Stack Manager  Alberto Carreno (ESA Houston)

Legal Issues
We need to secure the following:

Can an ESA employee execute the transaction on behalf of ENA?
